id: Watch live: Trump holds rally in Wisconsin
paragraph: President Trump on Wednesday night will hold a rally in Mosinee, Wis., for Republican candidates in the state.The event is scheduled to begin at 7:30 p.m.Watch the live video above. View the discussion thread.The Hill 1625 K Street, NW Suite 900 Washington DC 20006 | 202-628-8500 tel | 202-628-8503 faxThe contents of this site are ©2018 Capitol Hill Publishing Corp., a subsidiary of News Communications, Inc.
